Class GUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • GUI

  • public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object
    Graphical user interface to draw graphs in different layouts. Graphs are loaded from a txt-file and can be visualized with the following layouts:
    • CircularEmbedding
    • GridEmbedding
    • LayeredEmbedding
    • LinearEmbedding
    • RandomEmbedding
    • SpectralEmbedding
    • SpringEmbedding
    Additional functionality such as displaying information about the graph and/or certain nodes, saving the currently displayed layout as a picture or zooming is also provided.
    Version:
    1.0.1, 13rd June 2019
    Author:
    Clemens Hofstadler, Lukas Wögerer
